addAsset(address,address).details: Adds a new sellable asset to the marketplace

params.asset: Address of the asset to add
params.manager: Address of the asset's manager (or asset's address if asset doesn't have manager)

createListing(address,uint256,uint256,ui.details: Creates a new marketplace listing with the given price and quantity

params.asset: Address of the token for sale
params.tokenClass: The class of the asset's token

getListingIndex(address,address).details: Given the address of a user and an asset, returns the index of the marketplace listing

returns._0: uint Index of the user's marketplace listing

getMarketplaceListing(uint256).details: Given the index of a marketplace listing, returns the listing's data

returns._0: (address, address, uint, uint, uint) Asset for sale, address of the seller, asset's token class, number of tokens for sale, USD per token

purchase(address,uint256,uint256).details: Purchases the specified number of tokens from the marketplace listing

params.asset: Address of the token for sale

removeListing(address,uint256).details: Removes the marketplace listing at the given index

params.asset: Address of the token for sale

updatePrice(address,uint256,uint256).details: Updates the price of the given marketplace listing

params.asset: Address of the token for sale

updateQuantity(address,uint256,uint256).details: Updates the number of tokens for sale of the given marketplace listing

params.asset: Address of the token for sale

addAsset(address,address).notice: Meant to be called by whitelisted contractSet 'manager' to asset address if asset doesn't have manager

getListingIndex(address,address).notice: Returns 0 if user doesn't have a listing in the given asset
